Marcelle Monthil https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcelle_Monthil 0 Marcelle Monthil (8 June 1892 – 8 November 1950) was a French film actress. Born Marcelle Madeleine Montalenti in the Principality of Monaco, she died in Paris. Marcelle_Monthil ( 8_June_1892 – 8_November_1950 ) was a_French_film_actress .
